            <div corresp="#c5805f2">
                <head>Latvia.</head>
                <p>John Sterett Gittings Jr., en route to this post, was permitted to remain two
                    weeks in London; He was then directed to proceed to Stockholm on temporary
                    assignment to assume charge on departure of Meyers, on leave. To remain
                    Stockholm until shortly after return of Minister Bliss. Then to proceed to
                    Riga.</p>
